1.5 - 1/24/2024
- Fixed virtual keyboard styles not being applied.
- Fixed some buttons and headings being misaligned or too big in the QAM.
- Fixed several elements no longer being enlarged due to changes in the game mode UI.
- Improved sizing and alignment of text and icons on the in-game controller map screen (still not great, but better.)
- Tweaked Storage page element sizing.
- Increased game title and info labels on Home tab.
- Added sizing tweaks to the Downloads tab. They might still be kinda janky.

